    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285390/extras/8ed6c58669fa8e78cd2ae634e2b6bf89.avif?t=1748869224\" width=600 height=155 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285390/extras/c76cdc9b907816f38d0c70096a0b4bfe.avif?t=1748869224\" width=600 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lhama Clicker</strong> 是一款放置点击游戏，关于<strong>繁殖</strong> <strong>无限</strong>数量的羊驼。为了将你的生产力提升到<strong>荒谬的水平</strong>，你需要购买升级、提升等级、购买<strong>星界升级</strong>，并多次<strong>重生</strong>以变得<strong>更快更强</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这段冒险中，你<strong>也</strong>将解锁如羊驼皮肤、美丽帽子和全新背景等装饰性元素。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285390/extras/8c2f6ef2578f9f13734047a6379992d2.avif?t=1748869224\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285390/extras/48a36a7a12b5bcd7a63a3b6b3581a743.poster.avif?t=1748869224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285390/extras/48a36a7a12b5bcd7a63a3b6b3581a743.webm?t=1748869224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285390/extras/48a36a7a12b5bcd7a63a3b6b3581a743.mp4?t=1748869224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285390/extras/73f210015c834430e43d43338ee0deee.avif?t=1748869224\" width=600 height=73 /></span><span class=